lead_paragraph: The Chiefs held on grimly to stave off a late assault by the visiting Sharks and maintain top spot in the Super Rugby standings after an energy-sapping 24-22 win in New Plymouth on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Chiefs Survive Shark Attack to Stay Top in Super Rugby
headline.main: Chiefs Survive Shark Attack to Stay Top in Super Rugby
